Features:
Budget Tracking: Set monthly budgets for each category in Rands

Expense Logging: Track all your expenses with descriptions

Visualizations: See pie charts and bar graphs of your spending

Financial Advice: Get personalized advice based on your spending patterns

Monthly Reports: Detailed breakdowns of your finances

Data Persistence: Automatically saves and loads your data

Savings Tracking: Monitor progress toward your savings goals

How to Use:
Start by setting your monthly income

Set budget limits for each category

Add expenses as you spend money

Use the menu to:

View summaries

Get financial advice

Generate reports

Update budgets

Visualize your spending

Tips for Financial Management:
Recommended Budget Allocation (as percentage of income):

Savings: 20%

Groceries: 15-20%

Transportation: 10-15%

Toiletries: 3-5%

Personal Care (Haircuts): 2-5%

Clothing: 5-10%

Other: 5-10%

Save your data regularly - it automatically saves to finance_data.json

Review your spending weekly to stay on track

The software will help me visualize where my money goes each month and provide insights to improve my financial habits...